oai_dc:dc.dc:title: L.A. City Planning Department Publishes Final Animal Regulations
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: n/a, n/a
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Los Angeles City Planning Departmenthas submitted its final draft of theproposed ordinance to restrict the numberof gamebirds, waterfowl and othersmall birds and mammals to be allowedon residential property within the City ofLos Angeles. The proposed ordinance willbe submitted for public scrutiny beforethe City Planning Commission publichearing to be held Tuesday, June 24,1975, at 7 p.m., at the Northridge JuniorHigh School Auditorium, 17960 Chase,Northridge. California.
